ale and female characters are well-crafted and captivating, and the novel contains breathtaking descriptions of the natural beauty of the Croatian coast.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / General.2bisacsh  aCroatian literature.  aModernism.  aexistentialism.  apsychological drama.1 aJanigro, Damir, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertCentral European University Press eBook-Package 2023z978311079759640uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9789633867235?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9789633867235423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9789633867235/original  a978-3-11-079759-6  Central European University Press eBook-Package 2023b2023  aEBA_EMB  aGBV-deGruyter-alles